{"Title":"蒜香面包片的做法","Primary":["吐司2片","黄油15克","食盐1克"],"Auxiliary":["白皮蒜3瓣","罗勒1克"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.面包切去边","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223888820663.jpg","2.切成小方块状","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223889207074.jpg","3.黄油微波炉叮一下至溶化","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223890261156.jpg","4.加入切碎的蒜末和罗勒、少许盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223891377372.jpg","5.搅拌均匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223893012527.jpg","6.均匀涂在面包片上","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223895100918.jpg","7.间隔一定距离铺入烤盘","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223895695790.jpg","8.送入预热好的烤箱180度5分钟左右","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223896227853.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223898843450.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223899128472.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223899488224.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142223899689454.jpg","烹饪技巧","1、蒜切碎一点，捣成蒜泥也不错；2、吃完蒜喝点牛奶，可以清除嘴里的味道。"]}